cker.%20There%20have%20also%20been%20reports%20that%20the%20police%20cremated%20the%20body%20in%20a%20hurry%2C%20which%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20have%20denied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20been%20alleging%20that%20the%20police%20is%20involved%20in%20a%20massive%20cover-up%20to%20protect%20the%20guilty.%20Their%20allegation%20got%20a%20boost%20after%20a%20midnight%20attack%20on%20the%20hospital%20on%20August%2015%2C%20as%20the%20statewide%20women's%20%26quot%3BReclaim%20the%20Night%26quot%3B%20demonstration%20was%20on.%20With%20the%20attackers%20wrecking%20the%20emergency%20department%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20it%20was%20another%20attempt%20at%20obliterating%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20social%20media%20post%20today%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20claimed%20that%20the%20viscera%20of%20the%20doctor%20was%20%26quot%3Bchanged%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20by%20the%20Kolkata%20Police.%20He%20also%20alleged%20tampering%20of%20other%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20following%20information%20that%20I%20have%20gathered%20from%20my%20various%20reliable%20sources%20might%20be%20germane%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20Investigation%20undertaken%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCBIHeadquarters%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40CBIHeadquarters%3C%2Fa%3E%3A-%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20The%20viscera%20of%20the%20deceased%20victim%20Doctor%20has%20been%20changed%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKolkataPolice%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40KolkataPolice%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20name%20of%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20(%40SuvenduWB)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSuvenduWB%2Fstatus%2F1824808405921649146%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EAugust%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fbloc