ospital%20has%20no%20on-call%20room.%20Apparently%20she%20had%20dropped%20off%20to%20sleep%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20partially%20clothed%20body%2C%20bearing%20multiple%20injuries%2C%20was%20found%20there%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20suspect%20is%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20with%20Kolkata%20Police%20who%20was%20stationed%20at%20the%20police%20outpost%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20and%20had%20access%20to%20all%20departments.%20He%20was%20arrested%20on%20basis%20of%20CCTV%20footage%20that%20showed%20him%20entering%20the%20building%20where%20the%20doctor%20was%20found%20murdered.%20A%20Bluetooth%20headset%20found%20next%20to%20the%20victim's%20body%20was%20seen%20on%20his%20neck%20in%20the%20CCTV%20footage.%20It%20was%20found%20to%20be%20paired%20with%20his%20phone%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20has%20reported%20that%20Roy%20admitted%20to%20the%20crime%20soon%20after%20police%20started%20questioning%20him.%20%26quot%3BHang%20me%20if%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20told%20the%20police%20nonchalantly%2C%20the%20reports%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20views%20that%20it%20was%20not%20once%20person%20who%20attacked%20their%20daughter%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20saying%20that%20from%20the%20beginning.%20All%20the%20people%20we%20spoke%20to%2C%20even%20MBBS%20doctors.%20agreed%20thatit%20was%20not%20possible%20for%20one%20person%20to%20do%20as%20much%20was%20done%20to%20her%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saddest%20part%20of%20the%20whole%20matter%2C%20he%20said%2C%20was%20that%20the%20people%20who%20were%20supposed%20to%20ensure%20his%20daughter's%20safety%2C%20failed%20to%20discharge%20their%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20parents%2C%20we%20worry%20when%20our%20child%20is%20on%20the%20road%2C%20not%20so%20much%20when%20she%20reaches%20her%20workplace.%20Like%20we%20used%20to%20drop%20her%20to%20school.%20Once