n%20I%20saw%20her.%20There%20were%20no%20clothes%20on%20her%20body.%20She%20was%20only%20draped%20in%20a%20bedsheet.%20Her%20legs%20were%20apart%2C%20with%20one%20hand%20on%20her%20head.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20sparked%20nationwide%20protests%20across%20the%20country%20with%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20on%20strike%20for%2024%20hours%20from%20August%2017-18.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20lost%20everything%3B%20we%20have%20nothing%20left.%20We%20want%20justice%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20father%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rg-kar-hospital-trinamool-mp-summoned-by-cops-over-sniffer-dog-claim-in-rape-murder-probe-6363180%5C%22%3ETrinamool%20MP%20Summoned%20By%20Cops%20Over%20%26quot%3BSniffer%20Dog%26quot%3B%20Claim%20In%20Rape-Murder%20Probe%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20today%20conducted%20a%20psychological%20test%20of%20the%20prime%20suspect%2C%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20with%20Kolkata%20Police%20who%20was%20stationed%20at%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20on%20the%20night%20of%20the%20incident.%20Roy%20had%20access%20to%20all%20departments%2C%20and%20the%20CBI's%20team%2C%20including%20five%20experts%20from%20the%20Central%20Forensic%20Science%20Laboratory%20(CFSL)%2C%20is%20probing%20every%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMamata%20Banerjee%20Slammed%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20led%20a%20protest%20rally%20from%20Moulali%20to%20Dorina%20Crossing%20area%20of%20Kolkata%20on%20Friday%2C%20demanding%20justice%20for%20the%20woman%20doctor.%20She%20demanded%20that%20the%20culprits%20be%20hanged.%20Taking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20victim%20said%20that%20he%20has%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20Trinamool%20leader.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarly%20on%2C%20I%20had%20full%20faith%20in%20her%2C%20but%20now%2C%20no.%20She%20is%20asking%20for%20justice%2C%20but%20what%20is%20she%20saying%20that%20for%3F%20She%20can%20take%20charge%20of%20that%3B%20she%20is%20doing%20nothing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-takes-up-kolkata-doctor-rape-murder-case-chief-justice-led-bench-to-hear-matter-on-tuesday-6364251%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20Takes%20Up%20Doctor%20Rape-Murder%20Case%2C%20To%20Hear%20Matter%20On%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim's%20mother%2C%20standing%20next%20to%20her%20husband%2C%20slammed%20the%20much-touted%20welfare%20schemes%20introduced%20by%20Ms%20Banerjee's%20administration%2C%20which%20he%20dismissed%20as%20hollow%20promises.%20The%20mother%20used%20the%20goddess%20Lakshmi%20as%20a%20metaphor%20to%20question%20the%20schemes%20aimed%20at%20making%20the%20lives%20of%20women%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20schemes%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20-%20the%20%C2%A0Kanyashree%20scheme%2C%20the%20Lakshmi%20scheme%20-%20all%20pseudo.%20Whoever%20wants%20to%20avail%20of%20these%20schemes%2C%20before%20availing%20them%2C%20kindly%20see%20if%20your%20Lakshmi%20at%20home%20is%20safe%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEx%20Principal%20Being%20Probed%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20person%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20ongoing%20investigation%20is%20the%20former%20principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%2C%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20whose%20actions%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20crime%20are%20under%20scrutiny.%20Mr%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20resigned%20from%20his%20post%20just%20two%20days%20after%20the%20body%20was%20found%2C%20has%20been%20questioned%20by%20the%20CBI%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-bjp-leader-locket-chatterjee-2-doctors-summoned-over-fake-news-on-kolkata-rape-murder-6362250%5C%22%3EBJP%20Leader%2C%202%20Doctors%20Summoned%20Over%20'Fake%20News'%20On%20Kolkata%20Rape-Murder%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigators%20are%20examining%20his%20phone%20records%20and%20scrutinising%20his%20behaviour%20both%20before%20and%20after%20the%20incident.%20One%20key%20focus%20is%20why%20he%20made%20the%20victim's%20parents%20wait%20nearly%20three%20hours%20before%20allowing%20them%20to%20see%20their%20daughter's%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20also%20investigating%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20premeditation%20involved%20in%20the%20crime%20and%20whether%20the%20former%20principal%20had%20any%20role%20in%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723985280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fb7be7iqo_kolkata-case-_625x300_17_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkolkata-rape-murder-rg-kar-she-was-only-draped-in-bedsheet-father-of-kolkata-rape-murder-victim-6364313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20father%20of%20the%2031-year-old%20postgraduate%20trainee%20doctor%20who%20was%20found%20brutally%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20on%20August%209%20has%20described%20the%20devastating%20moment%20he%20discovered%20his%20daughter's%20body.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rape-Murder%20Victim's%20Father%20Releases%20Fury%20On%20Kolkata%20Hospital%20Over%20Safety%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%20junior%20doctor%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20in%20a%20Kolkata%20college%20and%20hospital%20has%20severely%20criticised%20the%20management%20for%20not%20ensuring%20safety%20at%20the%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grieving%20father%20of%20the%20young%20doctor%20whose%20life%20was%20cut%20short%20in%20a%20horrific%20and%20brutal%20way%20told%20NDTV%20that%20he%20trusted%20the%20college%20authorities%20to%20keep%20his%20daughter%20safe%20-%20as%20is%20expected%20of%20any%20professional%20workplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20place%20where%20I%20sent%20my%20daughter%20for%20her%20to%20make%20a%20living%20and%20serve%20the%20people%2C%20they%20did%20not%20protect%20her.%20It%20is%20very%20sad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20send%20our%20daughters%20to%20schools%2C%20colleges.%20Once%20they%20enter%20the%20gate%2C%20we%20do%20not%20know%20how%20they%20would%20be%20treated%2C%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20them.%20It%20was%20the%20same%20with%20the%20hospital%20where%20she%20worked%20too.%20She%20was%20on%20her%20own%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20said%20his%20daughter%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20by%20more%20than%20one%20suspect.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20impossible%20that%20only%20one%20suspect%20is%20involved.%20There%20are%20more%20suspects%20at%20large%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Kolkata%20Police%20issued%20summons%20to%20former%20BJP%20MP%20Locket%20Chatterjee%20and%20two%20doctors%20for%20allegedly%20spreading%20rumours%20and%20disclosing%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20woman%20doctor%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20at%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20also%20issued%20summons%20to%2057%20others%20for%20spreading%20wrong%20information%20about%20the%20crime%2C%20an%20officer%20said.%20Kolkata%20Police%20Commissioner%20Vineet%20Goyal%20told%20reporters%20a%20lot%20of%20rumour-mongering%20has%20affected%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20murdered%20doctor%20had%20claimed%20they%20were%20informed%20on%20phone%20on%20Augu