20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20over%20%24606%20million%20wagered%20on%20the%202024%20election%20on%20Polymarket%2C%20favoring%20a%20Harris%20win.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERutgers'%20Harry%20Crane%20said%20looser%20regulation%20would%20allow%20more%20participation%20and%20prevent%20manipulation.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20the%20outcome%20of%20an%20election%2C%20most%20look%20at%20polling%2C%20expert%20takes%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fstock-market-presidential-election-prediction-winner-donald-trump-kamala-harris-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeven%20the%20stock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20prediction%20markets%2C%20which%20allow%20bettors%20to%20wager%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20events%2C%20may%20be%20the%20most%20accurate%20way%20of%20calling%20the%20result%20ahead%20of%20November%205.%20They've%20successfully%20forecast%20the%20last%20few%20presidential%20cycles%20and%20even%20predicted%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20would%20drop%20out%20weeks%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20they're%20not%20without%20their%20misses%20%E2%80%94%20they%20were%20notably%20wrong%20during%20the%202022%20midterm%20elections%2C%20and%20after%20Biden%20won%20the%202020%20election%20%E2%80%94%20Rutgers%20University%20statistics%20professor%20Harry%20Crane%20says%20prediction%20markets%20are%20historically%20more%20accurate%20than%20traditional%20polling.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20month%2C%20a%20series%20of%20election-related%20events%E2%80%94an%20attempted%20assassination%20against%20Trump%2C%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20stepping%20down%20and%20endorsing%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20and%20both%20candidates%20picking%20their%20running%20mates%E2%80%94have%20adjusted%20polling%20considerably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Crane%20says%20these%20adjustments%20are%20often%20reflected%20in%20prediction%20markets%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolymarket%2C%20a%20crypto-based%20betting%20market%2C%20predicted%20a%2070%25%20chance%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20would%20drop%20out%20of%20the%20race%20this%20year%20as%20far%20back%20as%20July%204%2C%20two%20weeks%20before%20he%20actually%20bowed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20event-driven%20market.%20So%20the%20past%20month%20has%20been%20very%20active%20because%20events%20have%20occurred%20that%20are%20of%20extreme%20significance%2C%26quot%3B%20Crane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20markets%20will%20likely%20get%20even%20quicker%20at%20factoring%20in%20new%20information%20on%20election%20night%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20vote%20totals%2C%20exit%20polls%2C%20and%20absentee%20ballots%20come%20in%2C%20prediction%20markets%20%26quot%3Bmove%20pretty%20significantly%20and%20pretty%20quickly%20in%20response%20to%20that%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227dc81ce7-8b15-46b0-8923-323c06d08f5d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20user%20base%20is%20(literally)%20invested%20in%20the%20outcome%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20range%20of%20participants%20in%20betting%20markets%2C%20and%20most%20are%20making%20highly%20informed%20wagers%2C%20Crane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20recreational%20bettors%20who%20may%20just%20have%20an%20interest%20in%20whatever%20topic%20is%20up%20for%20debate%2C%20as%20well%20as%20professional%20bettors%20and%20betting%20syndicates%20whose%20livelihoods%20are%20at%20stake.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20companies%20looking%20to%20hedge%20risk%20if%20they%20may%20be%20affected%20by%20candidates'%20proposed%20policies.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpolymarket.com%2Fevent%2Fpresidential-election-winner-2024%3Ftid%3D1723813625985%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24606.5%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20riding%20on%20the%20election%20outcome%20on%20Polymarket%20alone%2C%20participants%20watch%20the%20news%20closely%2C%20Crane%20said.%20Even%20if%20they%20aren't%20based%20in%20the%20US%2C%20they%20are%20just%20as%20clued%20into%20election%20updates%20since%20their%20money%20is%20on%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20likens%20it%20to%20sports%20betting%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20a%20professional%20football%20player%20to%20know%20how%20to%20understand%20what's%20going%20to%20happen%20in%20a%20football%20game.%20And%20in%20fact%2C%20I%20could%20be%20better%20at%20it%20than%20players%20in%20the%20game%20from%20a%20betting%20or%20informational%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fb2c38a6-7896-42bc-9923-760bf527f3ee%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHigher%20participation%20could%20boost%20accuracy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECrane%20says%20that%20prediction%20markets%20could%20become%20even%20more%20accurate%E2%80%94%20and%20avoid%20any%20potential%20risk%20of%20manipulation%20by%20political%20groups%20%E2%80%94if%20they%20are%20fully%20legalized%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20popular%20prediction%20markets%20are%20largely%20unavailable%20to%20US%20participants.%20US-based%20users%20can't%20bet%20on%20Polymarket%2C%20and%20Betfair%2C%20one%20of%20the%20longest-running%20events%20markets%2C%20is%20only%20available%20in%20some%20US%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPredictIt%2C%20a%20project%20founded%20by%20researchers%20in%20New%20Zealand%2C%20has%20operated%20in%20the%20US%20under%20a%20no-action%20letter%20from%20the%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%20since%202014%2C%20but%20limits%20American%20bettors%20to%20up%20to%20%24850%20in%20wagers%2C%20and%20only%205%2C000%20betters%20can%20participate%20in%20each%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPredictIt%20is%20facing%20headwinds%20from%20the%20CFTC%2C%20which%20is%20looking%20to%20outlaw%20all%20election%20betting.%20If%20passed%2C%20Americans%20wouldn't%20be%20legally%20allowed%20to%20participate%20in%20any%20prediction%20markets%2C%20though%20some%20may%20try%20using%20VPNs%20to%20bypass%20