Finke%20and%20John%20Hussman%20highlight%20the%20risks%20of%20investing%20at%20peak%20valuations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20investing%20advice%20that%20you've%20probably%20heard%20over%20and%20over%20again%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-invest-in-index-funds%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20an%20index%20fund%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20don't%20touch%20it%2C%20and%20watch%20your%20nest%20egg%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20good%20reason.%20History%20has%20proven%20this%20to%20be%20a%20brilliant%20strategy%20if%20investors%20are%20willing%20to%20hold%20for%20the%20long%20term.%20For%20example%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.officialdata.org%2Fus%2Fstocks%2Fs-p-500%2F1990%3Famount%3D100%26endYear%3D2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24100%20invested%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%201990%20would%20be%20worth%20%243%2C220%20today.%20Returns%20on%20index%20funds%20tracking%20major%20indexes%20have%20been%20so%20good%20while%20requiring%20minimal%20effort%20that%20they're%20where%20investing%20legend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwarren-buffett-best-investment-advice-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWarren%20Buffett%20tells%20most%20people%20to%20put%20their%20money%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOdds%20are%20this%20approach%20will%20continue%20to%20succeed%20over%20a%20multi-decade%20period.%20This%20is%20even%20more%20the%20case%20for%20investors%20who%20dollar-cost-average%2C%20or%20buy%20in%20increments%20over%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20during%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20evidence%20shows%20that%20it's%20an%20utterly%20terrible%20time%20to%20buy%20into%20the%20broader%20market%2C%20especially%20for%20investors%20looking%20to%20hold%20for%20around%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20a%20bold%20statement%2C%20considering%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20is%20up%2025%25%20over%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that's%20just%20it.%20The%20market%20has%20gotten%20so%20frothy%20in%20terms%20of%20valuation%20that%20it's%20setting%20itself%20up%20for%20abysmal%20returns%20over%20the%20next%2010%20or%20so%20years.%20That's%20what%20the%20numbers%20say%2C%20at%20least.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EValuations%20measure%20how%20expensive%20stocks%20are%20relative%20to%20history.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20common%20gauges%20is%20the%2012-month%20forward%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%2C%20which%20considers%20the%20price%20of%20a%20stock%20or%20the%20overall%20market%20relative%20to%20near-term%20earnings%20expectations.%20There's%20also%20the%20price-to-earnings-to-growth%20ratio%20(PEG)%2C%20which%20considers%20longer-term%20growth%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20determining%20long-term%20returns%2C%20other%20metrics%20prove%20to%20be%20more%20trustworthy%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20determining%20how%20stocks%20will%20perform%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20Shiller%20cyclically-adjusted%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%20(CAPE)%2C%20which%20is%20a%2010-year%20rolling%20average%20of%20the%2012-month%20trailing%20PE%20ratio.%20This%20normalizes%20the%20measure%20by%20smoothing%20out%20outlier%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20analysis%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.advisorperspectives.com%2Farticles%2F2020%2F07%2F20%2Fthe-remarkable-accuracy-of-cape-as-a-predictor-of-returns-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMichael%20Finke%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20wealth%20management%20at%20The%20American%20College%20of%20Financial%20Services%2C%20the%20CAPE%20ratio%20has%20a%20remarkable%20ability%20to%20predict%20future%20returns.%20In%202020%2C%20Finke%20ran%20a%20regression%20analysis%2C%20a%20statistical%20test%20that%20aims%20to%20identify%20the%20impact%20that%20certain%20variables%20have%20on%20a%20given%20outcome%2C%20and%20found%20that%20between%201995%20and%202010%2C%20CAPE%20ratio%20levels%20at%20any%20point%20in%20time%20explained%2090%25%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20returns%20over%20the%20following%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221564%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CAPE%20ratio%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf9ac7b4912df3ae1c6791%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Finke%2FAdvisor%20Perspectives%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20between%20the%20CAPE%20ratio%20and%20future%20returns%20bodes%20poorly%20for%20the%2010%20years%20ahead.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20current%20CAPE%20ratio%20is%2035.7%2C%20trailing%20only%201999%20and%202021%20levels%20and%20sitting%20above%20the%20heights%20reached%20in%20the%201929%20bubble.%20A%20level%20of%2035.7%20puts%20estimated%20annualized%20returns%20over%20the%20next%20decade%20at%20around%203%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22shiller%20pe%20ratio%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bf9b335da406397bf6a812%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22380%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGuruFocus%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20that%20may%20not%20sound%20so%20bad%2C%20the%20benchmark%20index%20has%20doled%20out%2010.9%25%20annualized%20returns%20since%202008.%20Plus%2C%2010-year%20Treasury%20notes%20offer%20a%20risk-free%20annualized%20yield%20of%203.89%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Finke%20published%20his%20report%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D75f7157d9e18cf4ec1a35817c957e29be930d9ee913e4d8c60170b450a9e20b2%26postID%3D66bd1851b9a365362650169d%26postSlug%3Dsp500-index-funds-stock-market-valuations-cape-ratio-future-returns-2024-8%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.morningstar.com%252Fcolumns%252Frekenthaler-report%252Fmaybe-theres-something-shiller-cape-ratio-after-all%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22