%20card%20for%20a%20trip%20versus%20Affirm%20or%20Klarna%2C%20where%20it%20comes%20out%20of%20my%20bank%20account%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20think%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Hailee%20Gilmore%20told%20BI.%3Cp%3EHailee%20Gilmore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20third%20of%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennials%20said%20they%20don't%20feel%20%26quot%3Bfinancially%20stable%26quot%3B%20in%20Credit%20Karma's%20survey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHailee%20Gilmore%2C%2027%2C%20isn't%20one%20of%20them.%20She%20and%20her%20husband%20share%20a%20two-year-old%20child%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20student%20debt.%26quot%3B%20But%20they%20both%20work%20two%20jobs%20each%2C%20with%20Hailee%20earning%20about%20%2485%2C000%20annually%20from%20her%20full-time%20position%20at%20the%20New%20York%20State%20Health%20Department%20and%20her%20part-time%20job%20at%20a%20car%20dealership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20this%20stable%20stream%20of%20income%2C%20Gilmore%2C%20like%20Roby%2C%20said%20she%20would%20likely%20use%20buy-now%2C%20pay-later%20services%20to%20book%20vacations%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20them%2C%20Gilmore%20%E2%80%94%20who%20also%20said%20she%20grew%20up%20%26quot%3Bpoor%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20had%20been%20fronting%20travel%20costs%20on%20credit%20cards%2C%20although%20not%20to%20the%20same%20carefree%20degree%20as%20Roby.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20making%20a%20bad%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20Gilmore%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20irresponsible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20initially%20skeptical%20of%20Affirm%20and%20Klarna%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20until%20it%20came%20time%20to%20book%20her%20and%20her%20husband's%20almost%20%243%2C200%20honeymoon%20at%20a%20luxury%20all-inclusive%20resort%20in%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20didn't%20have%20the%20money%20for%20it.%20She%20suggested%20using%20Affirm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%20they%20did%2C%20booking%20their%20