nk%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20lost%20my%20wife%20to%20cancer%20last%20year.%20I'm%20heartbroken%20and%20facing%20a%20mountain%20of%20medical%20debt%20%E2%80%94%20I%20have%20no%20idea%20how%20to%20move%20forward%20and%20pay%20all%20of%20this%20off%20on%20my%20modest%20salary.%20My%20wife%20made%20most%20of%20our%20money%20when%20she%20was%20still%20working.%20I%20have%20enough%20to%20keep%20myself%20afloat%2C%20but%20I%20have%20nothing%20left.%20What%20do%20I%20do%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOverwhelmed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Overwhelmed%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20position%20you%20have%20found%20yourself%20in%20is%20terribly%20unfair.%20No%20one's%20grief%20should%20come%20with%20an%20invoice.%20But%20I'll%20refrain%20from%20going%20on%20a%20tirade%20about%20the%20impossible%20state%20of%20healthcare%20in%20the%20U.S.%20and%20instead%20give%20you%20actionable%20steps%20for%20conquering%20the%20mountain%20of%20medical%20debt%20so%20that%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20you%20can%20grieve%20in%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20this%20advice%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20my%20father-in-law%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20hospital%2C%20who%20knows%20all%20the%20inside%20tricks%20for%20figuring%20out%20your%20medical%20debt.%20First%2C%20he%20says%20you%20should%20never%20immediately%20cut%20a%20check.%20Treating%20medical%20bills%20like%20every%20other%20form%20of%20debt%20can%20be%20easy%20%E2%80%94%20responsible%20people%20just%20pay%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20between%20hospitals%20setting%20prices%20that%20health%20insurance%20companies%20will%20inevitably%20negotiate%20down%20and%20often%20having%20avenues%20of%20aid%20for%20people%20in%20difficult%20financial%20circumstances%2C%20many%20people%20don't%20realize%20that%20there%20is%20typically%20wiggle%20room%20at%20the%20bottom%20line.%20So%20there's%20no%20reason%20to%20rush%20right%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20father-in-law%20suggests%20calling%20the%20hospital%20and%20speaking%20to%20someone%20in%20the%20billing%20department.%20Every%20hospital%20will%20be%20different%2C%20but%20many%20have%20foundations%20that%20can%20help%20you%20reduce%20your%20bill%20or%20write%20it%20off%20altogether.%20They%20may%20require%20you%20to%20demonstrate%20your%20need%20with%20an%20application%2C%20proof%20of%20income%2C%20a%20letter%2C%20or%20more.%20He%20says%20that%20the%20key%20to%20getting%20financial%20aid%20is%20to%20show%20that%20you%20are%20willing%20to%20cooperate%20in%20the%20payment%20process%20to%20whatever%20degree%20you%20can%20and%20to%20be%20honest%20about%20your%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20you%20don't%20qualify%20for%20debt%20relief%2C%20the%20provider%20you%20owe%20will%20almost%20certainly%20work%20with%20you%20on%20a%20manageable%20payment%20plan.%20After%20all%2C%20they%20would%20rather%20get%20paid%20a%20little%20over%20a%20long%20period%20than%20not%20get%20paid%20at%20all%20because%20you%20had%20to%20declare%20bankruptcy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou've%20likely%20already%20considered%20this%2C%20but%20you%20could%20also%20put%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Flife-insurance%2Fbest-life-insurance-companies%5C%22%3Elife%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20payout%20you%20received%20after%20your%20wife's%20passing%20toward%20the%20hospital%20bills.%20Going%20from%20a%20dual%20income%20to%20a%20smaller%20single%20income%20will%20be%20a%20hard%20enough%20adjustment%20for%20you%2C%20so%20removing%20the%20medical%20debt%20from%20the%20equation%20will%20give%20you%20more%20space%20to%20rework%20your%20budget%20into%20something%20that%20can%20sustain%20your%20new%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20asked%20my%20friend%20Blaise%20Cannon%20about%20your%20situation%3B%20as%20the%20father%20of%20a%20child%20with%20a%20congenital%20disease%2C%20he's%20unfortunately%20become%20something%20of%20an%20expert%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fdoes-medical-debt-affect-credit-score%5C%22%3Emedical%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20first%20advice%20was%20the%20same%20as%20my%20father-in-law's%3A%20Never%20pay%20immediately.%20You%20have%20the%20right%20to%20verify%20everything.%20Verifying%20your%20bill%20will%20require%20an%20itemized%20list%2C%20so%20call%20and%20request%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20itemized%20bill%20they%20send%20you%20is%20written%20in%20insurance%20codes%2C%20call%20again%20and%20request%20one%20written%20in%20plain%20language.%20Once%20you%20receive%20this%20bill%2C%20check%20for%20surprise%20charges%20or%20services%20you%20don't%20remember%20receiving.%20Email%20or%20call%20the%20billing%20department%20to%20clarify%20anything%20you%20don't%20understand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECannon%20also%20encouraged%20you%20to%20know%20your%20rights.%20For%20instance%2C%20you%20cannot%20be%20billed%20out-of-network%20for%20an%20emergency%20in-patient%20stay.%20And%20if%20you%20have%20insurance%2C%20you%20should%20never%20agree%20to%20advance%20payment%2C%20because%20getting%20your%20insurance%20to%20reimburse%20you%20will%20be%20a%20brutal%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20suggested%20negotiating%20every%20bill%20every%20time.%20This%20can%20be%20a%20difficult%20mindset%20to%20adopt%20since%20most%20of%20our%20bills%20in%20life%20aren't%20up%20for%20discussion%2C%20but%20hospitals%20typically%20build%20these%20negotiations%20into%20their%20prices.%20For%20instance%2C%20Cannon%20said%20you%20can%20offer%20to%20pay%20a%20smaller%20amount%20upfront%20rather%20than%20getting%20on%20a%20payment%20plan%20for%20the%20total%20cost.%20If%20you%20get%20on%20a%20payment%20plan%2C%20insist%20on%20an%20autopay%20discount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20Cannon%20told%20me%20that%20he's%20learned%20time%20and%20again%20always%20to%20check%20your%20monthly%20bills.%20Since%20payment%20plans%20are%20often%20farmed%20out%20to%20third-party%20vendors%2C%20mistakes%20aren't%20rare%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20get%20overcharged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20make%20the%20necessary%20phone%20calls%2C%20go%20through%20the%20pile%20of%20invoices%2C%20and%20begin%20traversing%20this%20mountain%20of%20debt%2C%20I%20hope%20you%20find%20the%20space%20to%20take%20care%20of%20yourself%2C%20too.%20Money%20seems%20to%20make%20the%20world%20go%20'round%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it's%20so%20easy%20to%20get%20swept%20away%20by%20financial%20anxiety%2C%20even%20when%20a%20thousand%20other%20things%20deserve%20our%20time%20and%20attention.%20But%20you%20lost%20your%20life%20partner.%20Right%20now%2C%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20move%20forward%20as%20a%20person%20is%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20you%20can%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELooking%20for%20advice%20on%20how%20your%20savings%2C%20debt%2C%20or%20another%20financial%20challenge%20is%20affecting%20your%20relationships%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-find-financial-advisor%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20that%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%2