eymoon%20to%20visit%20my%20parents%20in%20their%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-tiny-home-rentals-escape-homes-tampa-florida-community-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enew%20Florida%20home%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2d1c2c5-443c-4301-85aa-93d9582bc8f7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20son's%20wedding%20was%20much%20more%20detailed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20journey%20in%20David%20and%20Lindsey's%20wedding%20preparations%20would%20play%20out%20a%20little%20differently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20they%20were%20engaged%2C%20wedding%20planning%20immediately%20kicked%20off%2C%20with%20the%20bride%20and%20groom%20creating%20multiple%20spreadsheets%2C%20assembling%20thick%20binders%20of%20wedding%20materials%2C%20establishing%20a%20website%20and%20registry%2C%20and%20scheduling%20Zoom%20meetings%20with%20potential%20vendors.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20Andy%20and%20I%20vowed%20to%20make%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20transform%20our%20mentality%2C%20put%20our%20judgmental%20attitudes%20aside%2C%20and%20completely%20support%20their%20very%20traditional%20plans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20they%20were%20so%20organized%20and%20seemed%20to%20have%20everything%20covered%2C%20Andy%20and%20I%20were%20focused%20on%20getting%20our%20own%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-dress-shopping-what-to-know-before-bridal-appointment-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewedding%20apparel%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20I%20was%20particularly%20anxious%20about%20this%20because%20I%20lacked%20experience%20purchasing%20formal%20attire%20and%20didn't%20want%20to%20screw%20it%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc772839-5b9b-4a99-b8a6-133860fce5be%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EFinding%20an%20outfit%20was%20anxiety-inducing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20conferring%20with%20friends%2C%20two%20shops%20were%20identified.%20I%20arrived%20at%20Shop%20One%20and%20was%20paired%20with%20a%2020-something%20salesperson.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20as%20I%20was%20trying%20on%20a%20dress%2C%20she%20had%20to%20call%20over%20another%20salesperson%20to%20assist%20her%20in%20zippering%20it%20up%20over%20my%20boobs.%20She%20then%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20probably%20not%20wearing%20your%20best%20bra.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20I%20kind%20of%20was%2C%20because%20I%20knew%20I%20was%20going%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-wedding-dresses-outfits-people-wore-this-year-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edress%20shopping%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20day%2C%20I%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20no%2C%20definitely%20not%20my%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20left%20the%20shop%20and%20panicked.%20Would%20I%20ever%20find%20a%20suitable%20dress%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20recovering%20from%20the%20humiliating%20Shop%20One%20experience%2C%20I%20went%20to%20Shop%20Two.%20The%2060-something%20proprietor%20was%20much%20more%20familiar%20with%20dealing%20with%20mothers%20of%20grooms%2C%20including%20those%20with%20ill-fitting%20bras.%20She%20selected%20a%20few%20dresses%20that%20all%20looked%20fabulous.%20The%20chosen%20dress%20was%20an%20iridescent%20blue%2C%20weirdly%20similar%20in%20color%20to%20the%20douche%20I%20was%20given%20at%20City%20Hall%20back%20when%20I%20was%20a%20bride.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dress%20shopping%20was%20followed%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-shapewear-bodysuits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edecisions%20about%20shapewear%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20modern%20version%20of%20girdles%20from%20my%20mom's%20generation%2C%20now%20pushed%20by%20the%20Kardashians%20and%20other%20trustworthy%20sources.%20I%20hadn't%20considered%20shapewear%20before%20hearing%20Lindsey%20and%20her%20mom%20discuss%20the%20undergarments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20with%20all%20important%20decisions%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%20turned%20to%20book%20club%20members%20for%20expert%20advice.%20I%20texted%3A%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20have%20experience%20with%20shapewear%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20gals%20quickly%20responded.%20They%20confided%20that%20it's%20essential%20to%20get%20that%20flawless%20no-line%20look.%20So%20a%20few%20days%20later%2C%20I%20was%20in%20a%20Macy's%20dressing%20room%2C%20squeezing%20myself%20into%20a%20spandex%20casing%20and%20compressing%20my%20internal%20organs%20to%20achieve%20that%20oh-so-smooth%20result.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20resulting%20lack%20of%20oxygen%20induced%20a%20hallucination.%20Standing%20before%20me%20was%20my%20former%20college%20professor%2C%20Betty%20Friedan%20%E2%80%94%20the%20activist%20who%20helped%20spark%20the%20women's%20movement%20in%20the%201970s.%20She%20was%20shaking%20her%20head%20and%20frowning%20at%20me.%20I%20ditched%20the%20shapewear%20right%20then%20and%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAndy's%20shopping%20experience%20was%20a%20bit%20more%20laid-back.%20He%20selected%20the%20first%20suit%20he%20tried%20on%20and%20never%20considered%20shapewear.%20After%20one%20fitting%2C%20he%20was%20good%20to%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fdd96f52-1d9f-4768-afb1-1a94367ee6be%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20though%20my%20son%20and%20I%20had%20different%20wedding%20styles%2C%20I%20loved%20celebrating%20with%20him%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20following%20months%20involved%20lots%20of%20anxiety%2C%20decision-making%2C%20and%20festivities.%20We%20participated%20in%20family%20mee