d%20be%20unfair%20to%20blame%20her%20for%20this.%20Why%20is%20the%20support%20staff%20sent%20with%20the%20athlete%2C%20and%20the%20government%20sends%20them%20along%20with%20the%20player%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EWo%20sab%20wahan%20tafri%20karne%20gaye%20hai%20kya%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(have%20they%20gone%20there%20for%20tourism)%3F'%20Sanjay%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20athlete%20who%20has%20won%20three%20of%20her%20bouts%20has%20to%20concentrate%20on%20her%20game%2C%20the%20staff%20is%20supposed%20to%20keep%20all%20other%20details%20in%20check%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sanjay%20Singh%20told%20IANS%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20her%20first%20response%20since%20she%20got%20disqualified%20on%20August%207%2C%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20on%20Friday%20thanked%20members%20of%20her%20support%20staff%20Dr%20Wayne%20Patrick%20Lombard%2C%20coach%20Woller%20Akos%20and%20physiotherapist%20Ashwini%20Jeevan%20Patil%20along%20with%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)'s%20CMO%2C%20besides%20Dr%20Dinshaw%20Pardiwala%2C%20after%20her%20Paris%20Olympics%20campaign%20ended%20in%20a%20heartbreak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20was%20disqualified%20from%20the%2050kg%20category%20women's%20freestyle%20final%20for%20being%20100%20gm%20overweight%20in%20the%20second%20weigh-in%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20summit%20clash.%20However%2C%20she%20challenged%20the%20verdict%20in%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS)%20but%20things%20did%20not%20come%20out%20in%20her%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20criticism%20of%20her%20support%20staff%20for%20failing%20to%20cut%20down%20her%20weight%20for%20the%20final%20match%2C%20the%2029-year-old%20detailed%20their%20contribution%20to%20her%20life%20and%20thanked%20them%20for%20their%20unwavering%20support%20in%20her%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWoller%20Akos%3A%20Anything%20I%20write%20about%20him%20will%20always%20be%20less.%20In%20the%20world%20of%20Women's%20Wrestling%2C%20I%20have%20found%20him%20to%20be%20the%20best%20coach%2C%20best%20guide%20and%20best%20human%20being%2C%20able%20to%20handle%20any%20situation%20with%20his%20calmness%2C%20patience%20and%20confidence.%20He%20does%20not%20have%20the%20word%20impossible%20in%20his%20dictionary%20and%20he%20is%20always%20ready%20with%20a%20plan%20whenever%20we%20face%20a%20tough%20situation%20on%20or%20off%20the%20mat%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20times%20when%20I%20doubted%20myself%2C%20and%20was%20shifting%20away%20from%20my%20internal%20focus%20and%20he%20would%20know%20exactly%20what%20to%20say%20and%20how%20to%20bring%20me%20back%20on%20my%20path.%20He%20was%20more%20than%20a%20coach%2C%20he%20was%20my%20family%20in%20wrestling.%20He%20was%20never%20hungry%20to%20take%20credit%20for%20my%20victory%20and%20success%2C%20always%20humble%20and%20taking%20a%20step%20back%20as%20soon%20as%20his%20work%20was%20done%20on%20the%20mat%2C%26quot%3B%20Vinesh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20want%20to%20give%20him%20the%20recognition%20he%20much%20deserves%2C%20whatever%20I%20do%20will%20never%20be%20enough%20to%20thank%20him%20for%20his%20sacrifices%2C%20for%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20away%20from%20his%20family.%20I%20can%20never%20repay%20him%20for%20the%20time%20lost%20with%20his%20two%20small%20boys.%20I%20wonder%20if%20they%20know%20what%20their%20father%20has%20done%20for%20me%20and%20if%20they%20understand%20how%20important%20his%20contributions%20have%20been.%20All%20I%20can%20do%20today%20is%20tell%20the%20world%20that%20if%20it%20hadn't%20been%20for%20you%20I%20would%20not%20have%20done%20on%20the%20mat%20what%20I%20have%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F8iu2vs21Wq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F8iu2vs21Wq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20(%40Phogat_Vinesh)%20%3Ca%20hr