ry%20package%20for%20freshers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20recent%20job%20posting%20for%20talent%20from%20non-engineering%20backgrounds%2C%20with%20a%203-year%20undergraduate%20degree%20has%20been%20grossly%20misrepresented.%20This%20job%20posting%2C%20with%20compensation%20of%20Rs%202.52%20lakhs%20annually%2C%20was%20only%20for%20candidates%20with%20a%203-year%20undergraduate%20degree%20and%20not%20for%20engineering%20graduates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20annual%20compensation%20for%20fresh%20engineering%20graduates%20ranges%20from%20Rs%204%20lakhs%20to%20Rs%2012%20lakhs%20annually%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20category%20of%20hiring%2C%20skill%20set%2C%20and%20advanced%20industry%20accredited%20certifications%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Surya%20Gummadi%2C%20EVP%20and%20President%2C%20Cognizant%20Americas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECognizant%20hires%20non-engineering%20undergraduate%20degree%20holders%20for%20administrative%20and%20other%20roles%20and%20invests%20substantial%20time%20and%20money%20in%20upgrading%20their%20skills%20and%20IT%20training%2C%20after%20which%20they%20get%20absorbed%20in%20various%20roles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20compensation%20we%20offer%20for%20engineering%20graduates%20is%20highly%20competitive%20within%20the%20IT%20services%20peer%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECognizant's%20salary%20package%20for%20engineering%20graduates%20matches%20the%20best%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20at%20some%20levels%2C%20it%20is%20even%20higher%20than%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20recruiting%20and%20upskilling%20freshers%20from%20engineering%20institutions%20as%20well%20as%20colleges%20offering%20degrees%20in%20science%2C%20arts%2C%20and%20commerce.%20Today%2C%20as%20AI%20increasingly%20powers%20modern%20businesses%2C%20we%20are%20creating%20new%20pathways%20for%20talent%20to%20thrive%20in%20India's%20technology%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Gummadi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGummadi%20--%20who%20joined%20Cognizant%20as%20a%20fresher%20two-and-half-decades%20back%20and%20rose%20through%20ranks%20to%20now%20head%20geography%2C%20which%20forms%20three-fourths%20of%20Cognizant's%20revenues%20--%20said%20the%20firm%20has%20a%20robust%20training%20programme%20that%20has%20benefited%20freshers%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20hire%20for%20entry-level%20roles%2C%20we%20invest%20approximately%20Rs%202%20to%203%20lakhs%20per%20associate%20in%20the%20initial%20years%20to%20train%2C%20mentor%20and%20upskill%20in%20advanced%20technologies.%20This%20is%20for%20both%20engineering%20and%20non-engineering%20associates.%20Hundreds%20of%20our%20associates%2C%20who%20joined%20us%20with%20a%203-year%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20today%20hold%20key%20positions%20from%20manager%20to%20assistant%20vice%20president%20across%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20annual%20increments%2C%20Cognizant%20said%20it%20works%20diligently%20to%20be%20competitive%20in%20its%20compensation%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20merit%20increases%20for%20this%20cycle%20are%20tied%20to%20both%20individual%20performance%20and%20macro%20industry%20dynamics.%20This%20year%2C%20we%20are%20one%20of%20the%20few%20IT%20companies%20in%20India%20that%20have%20delivered%20increments%20and%20bonuses%20for%20employees.%20This%20recent%20pay%20hike%20is%20the%204th%20that%20most%20Cognizant's%20associates%20have%20received%20in%20the%20past%203%20years.%20Moreover%2C%20these%20hikes%20are%20just%20one%20component%20of%20the%20comprehensive%20total%20rewards%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGummadi%20said%20Cognizant%20is%20a%20people-first%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20the%20heart%20of%20Cognizant%20and%20its%20largest%20talent%20hub%20-%20with%20over%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20its%20over%203%2C36%2C000%20global%20workforce%20-%20based%20in%20major%20metros%20and%20Tier-2%20cities%2C%20across%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20bring%20our%20offices%20closer%20to%20where%20our%20associates%20live%2C%20we%20have%20recently%20opened%20new%20centres%20in%20Bhubaneshwar%20and%20Indore%20and%20expanded%20operations%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Everything%20we%20do%20hinges%20on%20the%20quality%2C%20dedication%20and%20scale%20of%20our%20talent.%26quot%3B%20Over%20the%20past%20decades%2C%20the%20firm%20continued%20to%20unlock%20the%20full%20potential%20of%20the%20rich%20talent%20pool%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continuously%20invest%20in%20training%20and%20upskilling%20our%20associates%20in%20advanced%20digital%20technologies%2C%20sponsor%20higher%20education%20and%20leadership%20development%20programmes%20with%20top%20institutions%20so%20that%20our%20people%20are%20empowered%20to%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20innovation%2C%20learn%20the%20latest%20technologies%2C%20work%20with%20global%20clients%20and%20accelerate%20their%20career%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Cognizant%20has%20been%20recruiting%20and%20upskilling%20freshers%20from%20engineering%20institutions%20as%20well%20as%20colleges%20offering%20degrees%20in%20science%2C%20arts%2C%20and%20commerce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20as%20AI%20increasingly%20powers%20modern%20businesses%2C%20we%20are%20creating%20new%20pathways%20for%20talent%20to%20thrive%20in%20India's%20technology%20industry.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723964460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fcfe2oe78_cognizant_625x300_18_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-backlash-over-freshers-pay-cognizant-clarifies-what-techies-get-6362905%22%2C%22summary%22%3A