.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcx924r4d5yno%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20On%20immigration%2C%20Ms%20Harris%20has%20shifted%20towards%20bipartisan%20border%20security%20solutions%2C%20addressing%20the%20root%20causes%20of%20migration%20from%20Central%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Harris%20is%20a%20strong%20advocate%20for%20reproductive%20rights%20and%20has%20vowed%20to%20protect%20them%20nationwide%20if%20elected%20president.%20She%20also%20supports%20NATO%20and%20continued%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20while%20maintaining%20Israel's%20right%20to%20self-defence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20taxes%2C%20Ms%20Harris%20opposes%20increases%20for%20those%20earning%20under%20%24400%2C000%20and%20supports%20corporate%20tax%20rate%20hikes.%20She%20aims%20to%20expand%20healthcare%20access%20without%20eliminating%20private%20insurance.%20Ms%20Harris%20also%20supports%20gun%20safety%20regulations%2C%20including%20red-flag%20laws%2C%20to%20prevent%20gun%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723961700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F6v8dcj9_kamal-harris-childhood-photo_625x300_18_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwe-were-renters-kamala-harris-shares-story-behind-childhood-photo-6362199%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20pledge%20comes%20just%20ahead%20of%20the%20Democratic%20National%20Convention%20in%20Chicago%2C%20where%20Ms%20Harris%20is%20set%20to%20step%20onto%20the%20stage%20as%20the%20party's%20official%20presidential%20nominee%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwe-were-renters-kamala-harris-shares-story-behind-childhood-photo-6362199%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LIC%20agents%20earn%20Rs%2010k%20a%20month%20in%20HP%2C%20Rs%2020k%2Fmonth%20in%20Andaman%20%26amp%3B%20Nicobar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17239606110