E2%80%9D%20shares%20Nirbhik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20training%20under%20his%20physiotherapist%20for%208-10%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20Prateek%20carefully%20monitored%20how%20his%20bladder%20and%20stomach%20reacted%20to%20every%20bite%20of%20food%20and%20sip%20of%20liquid.%20%E2%80%9CRecovery%20involved%20a%20lot%20of%20trial%20and%20error.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20improvement%20comes%20slowly%2C%20but%20persistence%20is%20key%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202017%2C%20he%20could%20stand%20with%20a%20walker%20and%20perform%20tasks%20like%20cooking%2C%20and%20even%20use%20crutches.%20It%20was%20then%20that%20he%20wondered%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20should%20I%20stop%20living%20my%20life%20when%20my%20mind%20and%20spirit%20are%20free%20despite%20my%20challenges%3F%20I%20am%20ambitious%2C%20a%20big-time%20foodie%2C%20and%20love%20meeting%20my%20friends.%20Why%20should%20a%20wheelchair%20put%20an%20end%20to%20it%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetermined%20not%20to%20let%20his%20wheelchair%20limit%20him%2C%20he%20began%20reaching%20out%20to%20his%20friends%20after%20four%20years%20of%20isolation.%20%E2%80%9CThough%20they%20were%20initially%20unsure%2C%20they%20eventually%20realised%20I%20was%20still%20the%20same%20person%20and%20invited%20me%20back%20into%20their%20social%20circles%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20family%20struggled%20to%20find%20accessible%20locations%20for%20Prateek%2C%20so%20they%20took%20it%20upon%20themselves%20to%20install%20ramps.%20This%20way%2C%20he%20could%20join%20them%20in%20their%20outings%20to%20restaurants%20and%20theatres.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20goal%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20to%20start%20a%20big%20business%20but%20to%20improve%20accessibility%20for%20people%20like%20Prateek%2C%20helping%20them%20enjoy%20a%20life%20similar%20to%20anyone%20else%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nirbhik%2C%20adding%20that%20being%20able%20to%20go%20out%20for%20weekends%20and%20date%20nights%20boosted%20Prateek%E2%80%99s