lso%20promoted%20sustainable%20practices%20within%20the%20community.%20The%20project%20was%20completed%20by%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20their%20work%20was%20immediate%20and%20profound.%20The%20newly%20constructed%20toilets%20not%20only%20provided%20essential%20facilities%20but%20also%20triggered%20a%20behavioural%20change%20among%20the%20students.%20Built%20mainly%20for%20the%20boys%E2%80%99%20hostel%20at%20the%20campus%2C%20currently%20about%2080%20rural%20students%20including%20boys%20and%20girls%20are%20using%20these%20toilets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESriram%2C%20a%20Class%2012%20student%20of%20the%20school%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20when%20there%20were%20no%20toilets%2C%20I%20would%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20problems%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20night.%20As%20it%20is%20a%20forest%20area%2C%20I%20feared%20going%20out%20for%20urination.%20These%20new%20toilets%20have%20brought%20immense%20comfort%20to%20us.%20I%20really%20like%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20toilets%20and%20also%20the%20paintings%20made%20on%20them!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Michael%20who%20visited%20the%20school%20a%20month%20back%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20found%20the%20toilets%20were%20functioning%20properly.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20such%20issue%20of%20bad%20smell%20on%20campus%20and%20children%20are%20leading%20a%20regular%20school%20life.%20The%20improved%20sanitation%20conditions%20enhanced%20cleanliness%2C%20punctuality%2C%20and%20overall%20well-being%20of%20the%20school%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20hope%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F95712%2Fseva-mandir-rajasthan-ecosan-toilets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeco-toilets%20%3C%2Fa%3Espreads%20to%20schools%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20where%20students%20lack%20access%20to%20toilets.%20With%