Cp%3EThis%20dream%20had%20taken%20root%20when%20she%20was%20just%20a%20child%2C%20inspired%20by%20an%20article%20she%20read%20about%20a%20swimmer%20who%20had%20accomplished%20this%20incredible%20feat.%20Even%20before%20setting%20foot%20in%20a%20pool%2C%20the%2033-year-old%20took%20a%20bold%20step%20and%20registered%20herself%20for%20the%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tanvi%20stepped%20into%20a%20pool%20after%2018%20years%20in%202022.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Ftanvi-deore-1723814698-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-361692%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETanvi%20stepped%20into%20a%20pool%20after%2018%20years%20in%202022.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20she%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20making%20this%20dream%20a%20reality.%20In%20June%202024%2C%20she%20successfully%20swam%20the%20unforgiving%20waters%20from%20Dover%2C%20UK%2C%20to%20France%20in%2017%20hours%20and%2042%20minutes.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20she%20braved%20jellyfish%20stings%2C%20challenging%20tides%2C%20and%20the%20notorious%20%E2%80%98swimmer%E2%80%99s%20grave%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20circuit%20tha