ups%20and%20downs.%20Ajay%20and%20Angelica%20were%20no%20strangers%20to%20this.%20But%20ironically%20it%20was%20these%20sticky%20moments%20that%20gave%20Angelica%20an%20insight%20into%20her%20dad%E2%80%99s%20way%20of%20approaching%20problems.%20%E2%80%9CHis%20perspective%20is%20pretty%20cool%20as%20is%20his%20logical%20bend%20of%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20commends%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98We%20really%20talked%20our%20heart%20out%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPicture%20an%20expanse%20of%20white%20undulating%20terrain.%20The%20motorbike%E2%80%99s%20steady%20rumble%2C%20the%20whistling%20wind%2C%20and%20the%20chirp%20of%20a%20lone%20bird%20are%20the%20only%20things%20that%20interrupt%20the%20silence.%20Angelica%20would%20find%20these%20moments%20perfect%20for%20striking%20up%20a%20conversation%20with%20her%20father.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8UkB2a-N0BU%3Fsi%3DpgYk7ML1njdEw1Ch%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECity%20life%20has%20a%20mundaneness%20to%20it%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20live%20under%20the%20same%20roof%20but%20rarely%20have%20quality%20conversations.%E2%80%9D%20The%20bike%20rides%20flipped%20the%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98My%20dad%20began%20to%20see%20that%20he%20could%20count%20on%20me%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDeal%20breakers%E2%80%9D%20is%20how%20Angelica%20describes%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F347660%2Fsolo-travel-groups-the-flapper-life-zinal-doshi-experiential-travel-adventures-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20trips%3C%2Fa%3E%20she%20has%20taken%20with%20her%20father.%20Elaborating%20on%20this%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrior%20to