n%3Cp%3EShe%20aims%20to%20pursue%20a%20Bachelors%20degree%20in%20astrophysics%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20(IISc)%20or%C2%A0Indian%20Institute%20of%20Science%20Education%20and%20Research%20(IISER)%20or%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20you%20could%20also%20enrol%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rocketcenter.com%2FSpaceCamp%2FAdvancedAcademy%23block-usrcapiblock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espace%20camp%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%3A%20Geet%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723210097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fgeett-1723203096.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360476%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Geet%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Class%2011%20from%20Delhi%20participated%20in%20the%20NASA%20Space%20Camp%20at%20the%20US%20Space%20and%20Rocket%20Center%20in%20June%202024.%20Geet%20was%20just%20five%20when%20she%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20space.%20What%20followed%20soon%20was%20her%20ambition%20to%20become%20an%20astrophysicist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360476%2Fnasa-space-camp-for-students-astronauts-geet-alabama-us-space-rocket-centre-how-to-get-apply%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%20Uses%20Corn%20Waste%20to%20Make%20Bags%20That%20Decompose%20in%20180%20Days%3B%20Replaced%206%20Million%20Plastic%20Bags%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20when%20his%20peers%20engaged%20themselves%20in%20making%20social%20media%20content%2C%20Mohammed%20Azhar%20Mohiuddin%20saw%20this%20as%20an%20opportunity%20to%20delve%20into%20entreprene