dditionally%2C%20the%20company%20has%20expanded%20its%20focus%20to%20water%2C%20air%2C%20and%20soil%2C%20primarily%20relying%20on%20renewable%20resources%20and%20energy%20sources.%20Merino%20Industries%20is%20pursuing%20a%20%E2%80%98Water%20Neutrality%20Goal%E2%80%99%20through%20efficient%20water%20management%20practices%2C%20striving%20to%20reduce%20emissions%2C%20and%20implementing%20measures%20to%20improve%20air%20quality%20while%20minimising%20greenhouse%20gas%20(GHG)%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Lohia%20notes%20that%20while%20any%20industry%20would%20attempt%20to%20maximise%20production%20in%20additional%20land%20available%2C%20at%20Merino%2C%20green%20practices%20have%20always%20been%20the%20priority.%20This%20has%20led%20to%20the%20development%20of%20Miyawaki%20forests%20(multi-layered%20forests%20consisting%20of%20native%20plant%20species)%20on%20the%20campus%20at%20Hapur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20that%20trees%20are%20integral%20for%20clean%20air%2C%20habitat%20preservation%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20watershed%20protection%2C%20soil%20erosion%20prevention%2C%20and%20climate%20change%20mitigation%2C%20Merino%20has%20set%20a%20target%20to%20increase%20green%20cover%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20factory%20premises%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20planting%20of%20over%2020%2C000%20tree%20saplings%20throughout%20India%20during%202023-2024.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20to%20evolve%20as%20an%20industry%20but%20to%20do%20so%20sustainably.%20By%20blending%20expertise%20and%20resources%2C%20the%20company%20believes%20positive%20transformations%20can%20be%20driven%20in%20society.%20%E2%80%9COur%20strong%20belief%20is%20that%20by%20prioritising%20people%2C%20the%20planet%2C%20and%20sustainable%20product%20offerings%2C%20enterprises%20can%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mr%20Lohia%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723198670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Frenewable-energy-sources-1723194040.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360474%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sustainability%20at%20Merino%20Industries%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20mindset%20rather%20than%20an%20end%20goal%2C%20driving%20their%20commitment%20to%20eco-friendly%20practices%20and%20renewable%20energy%20alternatives.%20Their%20efforts%20have%20led%20to%2074.6%25%20of%20energy%20needs%20being%20met%20through%20green%20sources.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A283%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360474%2Fmerino-industries-renewable-green-energy-biomass-husk-solar-power-sustainable-company-practices%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MBA%20Couple%20Quit%20Corporate%20Life%20to%20%E2%80%98Move%20to%20The%20Hills%E2%80%99%2C%20Start%20Dreamy%20Organic%20Cafe%20in%20Uttarakhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20beat%20down%20on%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Barapullah%20flyover%20in%202017%2C%20a%20couple%20found%20themselves%20caught%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20decisive%20clarity.%20Amit%2C%20an%20employee%20at%20HDFC%20AMC%2C%20confided%20in%20his%20wife%20Shipra%2C%20an%20advertising%20professional%20at%20Outlook%20Magazine%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20this%20anymore.%20I%E2%80%99m%20resigning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20asked%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CWill%20you%20resign%20as%20well%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShipra%20nodded.%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20do%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20ahead%20was%20unclear%2C%20but%20their%20minds%20were%20made.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20knew%20we%20were%20going%20to%20follow%20our%20hearts%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Shipra%20now%20reflects%20that%20perhaps%20they%20should%20have%20made%20this%20move%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20the%20childhood%20friends%20had%20been%20craving%20something%20beyond%20the%20confines%20of%20a%20nine-to-five%20routine.%20Both%20had%20a%20passion%20for%20the%20natural%20world%20and%20organising%20forest%20trips.%20And%20they%20were%20both%20fond%20of%20food.%20They%20began%20to%20wonder%20if%20they%20could%20shape%20their%20lives%20around%20this%20shared%20passion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaving%20their%20careers%20in%20Delhi%20behind%2C%20with%20no%20back-up%20plan%2C%20Amit%20Kumar%20Srivastava%20and%20Shipra%20Mohan%20Sinha%20moved%20to%20Lansdowne%20in%20Uttarakhand%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-04-at-08.30.01-1_11zon-1-1723126572.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%26quot%3BWe%20knew%20we%20were%20going%20to%20follow%20our%20hearts%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Shipra%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-04-at-08.30.01-1_11zon-1-1723126572.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-04-at-08.30.01-1_11zon-1-1723126572-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-04-at-08.30.01-1_11zon-1-1723126572-500x667.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-04-at-08.30.01-1_11zon-1-1723126572-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-04-at-08.30.01-1_11zon-1-1723126572-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-04-at-08.30.01-1_11zon-1-1723126572-150x200.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360403%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20knew%20we%20were%20going%20to%20follow%20our%20hearts%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shipra%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20for%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20had%20first%20taken%20shape%20during%20Amit%E2%80%99s%20hiking%20trip%20to%20Tungnath.%20A%20local%20there%20had%20informed%20him%20of%20an%20old%20mule%20shed%20in%20Devikhal%20that%20was%20sitting%20idle.%20This%20spot%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20ideal%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20Amit%20and%20Shipra%20purchased%20it%20with%20their%20savings%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20small%20and%20cosy%20caf%C3%A9%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamed%20Lansdowne%20Trip%20Travel%20Caf%C3%A9%2C%20they%20thought%20of%20it%20as%20an%20experiment%20at%20first.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20only%20offered%20green%20tea%20and%20sandwiches%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remembers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%20had%20no%20visitors%20for%20the%20first%20six%20months%2C%20even%20with%20four%20locals%20on%20staff%20to%20keep%20the%20caf%C3%A9%20open.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20brought%20onboard%20young%20team%20members%20to%20help%20them%20with%20their%20educational%20expenses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20weekends%2C%20when%20they%20were%20not%20working%2C%20the%20couple%20used%20to%20travel%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Devikhal%20to%20train%20their%20team%2C%20hoping%20that%20the%20word%20would%20spread%20and%20attract%20more%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20goal%20was%20to%20create%20something%20distinctive%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311715%2Fbengaluru-social-impact-startup-mikro-grafeio-creates-employment-in-tier-ii-and-iii-indian-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovide%20jobs%20to%20the%20local%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Amit%20explains%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20noting%20the%20high%20migration%20rate%20from%20Devikhal.%20They%20aimed%20to%20reverse%20this%20trend%20by%20giving%20people%20reasons%20to%20return%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20they%20pulled%20off%20this%20mammoth%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAlways%20wanted%20to%20settle%20in%20the%20hills%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%2C%20who%20had%20been%20together%20since%20Class%2010%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358205%2Ftiny-farm-fort-homestay-rishikesh-raghav-ansh-kumar-delhi-architects-cob-sustainable-home%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealways%20knew%20they%20wanted%20to%20settle%20in%20the%20hills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20they%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20that%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuite%20surprisingly%2C%20their%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20USP%20was%20its%20continental%20food.%20Amit%20and%20Shipra%20taught%20their%20staff%20how%20to%20cook%20pizzas%2C%20pastas%2C%20and%20make%20milkshakes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20allure%20of%20having%20continental%20dishes%20in%20a%20village%20was%20fascinating%20to%20both%20locals%20and%20visitors%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caf%C3%A9%E2%80%99s%20popularity%20soared%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20flood%20of%20customers%20and%20a%20stream%20of%20positive%20reviews%20online.%20The%20scenic%20countryside%20view%20made%20waiting%20in%20line%20a%20pleasant%20experience%20for%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%202017%2C%20the%20couple%20relocated%20their%20caf%C3%A9%20to%20Lansdowne.%20The%20reason%3F%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20a%20remote%2C%20less%20commercialised%20location%20to%20create%20a%20truly%20unique%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shipra%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELansdowne%E2%80%99s%20dense%20forests%20were%20perfect%20for%20them%20%E2%80%94%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20close%20to%20nature%20and%20enjoy%20mountain%20treks.%20The%20area%E2%80%99s%20quiet%20charm%20and%20its%20closeness%20to%20their%20old%20place%20in%20Devikhal%20were%20also%20big%20pluses.%20Besides%2C%20they%20were%20confident%20that%20their%20loyal%20customers%20would%20make%20the%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201156px)%20100vw%2C%201156px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22They%20knew%20that%20Lansdowne%E2%80%99s%20dense%20forests%20were%20perfect%20for%20them.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958.jpeg%201156w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958-271x300.jpeg%20271w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958-500x554.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958-768x850.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-30-at-13.45.24_11zon-1723126958-150x166.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360410%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThey%20knew%20that%20Lansdowne%E2%80%99s%20dense%20forests%20were%20perfect%20for%20them.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20knew%20moving%20their%20caf%C3%A9%20to%20hill%20stations%20like%20Nainital%20or%20Mussoorie%20would%20be%20pricey.%20A%20piece%20of%20land%20in%20the%20cantonment%20area%20of%20Lansdowne%20was%20leased%20to%20them%20after%20they%20presented%20their%20plan%20to%20make%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20to%20the%20officials.%20Besides%2C%20the%20land%20was%20located%20away%20from%20the%20main%20market%20and%20thus%20had%20little%20interest%20