p%3EOn%2012%20June%202023%2C%20the%20results%20of%20the%20preliminary%20stage%20of%20the%20UPSC-CSE%20were%20scheduled%20to%20be%20announced.%20Unlike%20lakhs%20of%20aspirants%20awaiting%20the%20results%2C%20Vikas%20Kumar%20Meena%20had%20already%20believed%20that%20he%20would%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20list.%20He%20was%20so%20hopeless%20that%20he%20purchased%20the%20course%20for%20another%20competitive%20examination%2C%20minutes%20before%20the%20results%20were%20to%20be%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20no%20confidence%20that%20I%20would%20clear%20the%20prelims.%20I%20was%20so%20unmotivated%20that%20I%20tried%20shifting%20my%20focus%20to%20the%20SSC-CGL%20exam.%20I%20was%20busy%20solving%20the%20previous%20year%20questions%20for%20it%20when%20my%20friend%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20had%20checked%20the%20results.%20I%20was%20so%20scared%20that%20I%20wondered%20how%20I%20would%20face%20my%20family%20and%20relatives%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20few%20more%20minutes%2C%20I%20somehow%20gathered%20courage%20and%20found%20my%20name%20on%20the%20list.%20I%20checked%20my%20roll%20number%20at%20least%2020%20times.%20The%20happiness%20of%20clearing%20the%20UPSC%20prelims%20gives%20a%20different%20level%20of%20satisfaction%20altogether%20than%20clearing%20all%20subsequent%20stages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20behind%20his%20worry%2C%20Vikas%20says%2C%20was%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F235855%2Fupsc-topper-how-tips-method-irs-officer-failed-40-exams-inspiring-success-story-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHindi%20medium%20background%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20shatter%20the%20stereotypes%20by%20clearing%20the%20UPSC-CSE%202023%20examination%2C%20clenching%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%20672.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20now%20all%20set%20to%20undergo%20training%20as%20an%20Indi