all%20insect%20and%20feared%20losing%20my%20identity%20if%20I%20walked%20into%20that%20crowd%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20graduation%20in%202021%2C%20he%20started%20preparing%20for%20the%20examination.%20He%20clears%20a%20few%20misconceptions%20and%20shares%20helpful%20tips%20for%20aspirants%20based%20on%20his%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Psychological%20barriers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20says%20that%20firstly%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20are%20told%20to%20join%20coaching%20institutes%20because%20without%20it%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20succeed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20psychological%20aspects%20which%20get%20affected%20due%20to%20senior%20culture%20in%20the%20lanes%20of%20Mukherjee%20Nagar.%20New%20candidates%20are%20expected%20to%20seek%20guidance%20from%20those%20who%20have%20already%20given%20multiple%20attempts.%20So%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20%3Cem%3Ebhaiyaji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Esirji%20%3C%2Fem%3Eculture.%20They%20put%20blind%20faith%20in%20them%20and%20consider%20those%20who%20cleared%20the%20exam%20as%20god%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecondly%2C%20most%20of%20these%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants%20come%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F238088%2Fips-hero-upsc-cse-examination-tips-strategy-free-online-webinar-suraj-singh-parihar-police-instagram-facebook-twitter-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20income%20backgrounds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20is%20immense%20financial%20stress%20on%20them.%20I%20have%20seen%20many%20of%20my%20other%20aspirant%20friends%20working%20in%20libraries%2C%20ATMs%2C%20and%20catering%20services.%20They%20would%20hide%20their%20face%20and%20step%20out%20for%20work%20in%20order%20to%20afford%20their%20fee.%20They%20never%20felt%20confident%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-1-1723091305.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vikas%20cleared%20the%20UPSC-CSE%202023%20examination%20in%20his%20second%20attempt.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-1-1723091305.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-1-1723091305-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-1-1723091305-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-1-1723091305-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fvikas-1-1723091305-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360264%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVikas%20cleared%20the%20UPSC-CSE%202023%20examination%20in%20his%20second%20attempt.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Limited%20study%20material%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Vikas%20points%20out%20that%20compared%20to%20English%2C%20there%20is%20a%20limited%20study%20material%20for%20Hindi%20medium%20aspirants.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20there%20are%20standard%20books%20available%20in%20both%20languages%2C%20there%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20good%20study%20material%20for%20subjects%20like%20Environment%20and%20Ecology.%20I%20tried%20reading%20booklets%20offered%20by%20other%20coaching%20institutes%2C%20but%20I%20felt%20they%20had%20vocabulary%20and%20grammatical%20errors%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikas%2C%20who%20eventually%20referred%20to%20the%20booklet%20by%20the%20Shankar%20IAS%20academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Optimise%20sources%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5C